author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Solucom enters into a partnership with ShiftIN Partners
text:
Sept 22 Solucom SA :
* Enters into a partnership with ShiftIN Partners in the GCC
* Says ShiftIN Partners is a consulting firm headquartered in Abu Dhabi with offices in Dubai and Riyadh, that focuses on strategy execution and innovation management Source text: bit.ly/1j6LYdY Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
